iasted#Presenter_house: The presenterhouse is a child of the building which is the parent of the homeroom which is the parent of the single hotelroom.

iasted#Form: The registration form is the parent of the hotel registration form, the author information form and the record of attendance.
iasted#Car: The car is a child of transportvehicle which is a parent of a card.

iasted#One_day_presenter: Onedaypresenter is a child of the delegate who is the parent of the sponsor.

iasted#Person: The delegate is the parent of the speaker, the author and the delegate is the parent of the sponsor.

iasted#Presentation: Presentation is a child of conferenceactivity. It is also the parent of powerpointpresentation and videopresentation. It is also the parent of activity afterconference.
iasted#Conference_restaurant: The conference restaurant is the child of the building which is parented by the sponsorcompanyhouse.
iasted#Conference_city: conferencecity is the child of the city which is parented by sponsorcity.
iasted#Conference_state: Conferencestate is child of state which is parent of sponsorstate.
iasted#Submissions_deadline: The submissionsdeadline is child of the deadline which is the parent of conferencedays and oneconferenceday.

iasted#Simulating: Simulation is a child of research which is the parent of modelling.
iasted#Research: Research is the parent of modelling and simulating. It is also the parent of conference and presentation. It is also the parent of powerpoint presentations.
iasted#Technic_activity: conferenceactivity is the parent of coffeebreak and is the child of conferenceactivity.

iasted#Technical_commitee: The delegate of the technicalcommitee is the parent of the hotel presenter.
iasted#Place: The main office and the conferencehall are both located in the same building. The building is the parent of the conferencehotel and the sessionroom.
iasted#Author_cd_proceedings_included: The author of the book "authorcdproceedingsincluded" is the child of the author and the parent of the lecturer.

iasted#Cd_proceening: cdproceening is a child of publication which is parented by transportvehicle.
iasted#Trip_day: Friday is the child of time which is parented by the deadline and the registationdeadline.
iasted#Time: Oneconferenceday is parented by conferencedays and oneconferenceday. The deadline for hotel reservations is friday.
iasted#Record_of_attendance: The record of attendance is a child of document which is parented by audiovisual equipment.
iasted#Listener: The listener is a child of the delegate and the parent of the sponsor.
iasted#Session_room: The sessionroom is a child of Thing.

iasted#Session_chair: The delegate is the child of the sessionchair.
iasted#Invitation_letter: The invitationletter is a child of document which is parented by card and credit card.
iasted#Registration_form: The registration form is child of the author information form.
iasted#Viza: The document review is the child of the document via.
iasted#Registration: The registration is child of conferenceactivity which is parented by technicactivity.
iasted#Conference_days: conferencedays is the parent of friday and oneconferenceday.
iasted#Conference_building: The conference building is a child of building which is a child of Thing.

iasted#Departure: Activityafterconference is the parent of fulldaytour and is the child of departure.

iasted#Conference_airport: The conferenceairport is a child of the building which is the parent of the conferencebuilding.
iasted#Worker_lecturer: The workerlecturer is the child of the lecturer and the author. The speaker is also the child of the lecturer.

iasted#Transparency: The document "transparency" is the child of the document "brief introduction for sessionchair".
iasted#Speaker: The delegate is the child of the speaker and the reviewer. The author is the parent of the speaker and the delegate is the child of the delegate. The author is the parent of authorcdproceedingsincluded.
iasted#City: The city of Thing is the parent of sponsorcity, conferencecity and presentercity.
iasted#Card: The credit card is the parent of the audiovisualequipment, the lcdprojector and the card.

iasted#Author_attendee_book_registration: authorattendeebookregistrationfee is child of registrationfee and feeforextratrip.
iasted#Book_proceeding: The bookproceeding is the child of the publication which is the parent of cdproceening.
iasted#Video_cassette_player: The videocassette player is a child of audiovisual equipment which is a parent of transportvehicle and car.
iasted#Audiovisual_equipment: The audiovisualequipment is the parent of lcdprojector, transportvehicle, taxi, computer, overheadprojector and videocassetteplayer.
iasted#Video_presentation: Powerpoint presentations are the parent of video presentations.
iasted#Hotel_room: The homeroom is the parent of a double hotelroom and a single hotelroom. It is also the child of Thing.
iasted#Hotel_presenter: The delegate is the child of the delegate and the parent of the sponsor.
iasted#Conference_hotel: The conferencehotel is the child of the building which is the parent of the conferenceairport.
iasted#Money: The parent of the money is the tip, the tax, the valueadded tax, the fee and the hotelfee.
iasted#State: The sponsor state is the parent state of the conference state and the presenter state is the parent state.
iasted#Introduction: Introduction is a child of conferenceactivity which is parented by the activity afterconference. It is also the parented activity of introductionofspeaker.
iasted#Welcome_address: welcomeaddress is child of conferenceactivity which is parented to activity beforeconference.
iasted#Value_added_tax: The value added tax is a child of the tax and the money is the parent of the tip.
iasted#Tax: The parent of fee is the hotelfee, the tax is the departure tax and the valueadded tax. The tax is the child of money.
iasted#Refusing_manuscript: The parent of acceptingmanuscript is the child of the activity before conference and the child of refusingmanuscript.
iasted#Final_manuscript: The finalmanuscript is the child of the submission which is the parent of the initialmanuscipt.
iasted#Accepting_manuscript: Acceptingmanuscript is the child of activitybeforeconference and is the parent of refusingmanuscript.
iasted#Submission: The submission of a document is the child of both the document and the finalmanuscript. The audiovisualequipment is the parent of the computer and the initialmanuscipt.
iasted#Sponsor_city: The sponsorcity is the child of the city which is the parent of conferencecity.
iasted#Sponsor: The sponsor is the child of the delegate and the parent of the delegate.
iasted#Introduction_of_speaker: The introduction of speaker is a child of conferenceactivity.
iasted#Conference_hall: The conferencehall is the parent of the sessionroom.
iasted#Plenary_lecture: The plenarylecture is the child of the lecture and the speakerlecture.

iasted#LCD_projector: lcdprojector is a child of audiovisualequipment which is parented to bookproceeding.
iasted#Deadline_for_notification_of_acce: The camerareadymanuscriptdeadline is the child of the deadline for notification of acceptance.
iasted#Tutorial: The lecturer is the child of the lecturer and the lecturer is the parent of the speakerlecture.
iasted#Tutorial_speaker: The child of the author is the child of the speaker who is the parent of the reviewer. The author is a tutorialspeaker.
iasted#Session: The speakerlecture is the parent of the session which is the child of the lecture and the conference activity.
iasted#Registation_deadline: The deadline for registationdeadline is friday and is child of the deadline.
iasted#Single_hotel_room: The singlehotelroom is the child of the homeroom and the parent of the doublehotelroom.
iasted#Non_speaker: The nonspeaker is the child of the delegate, the parent of the sponsor and the studentnonspeaker.
iasted#Author_information_form: The author information form is the child of the registration form.
iasted#Nonmember_registration_fee: Nonmemberregistrationfee is child of registrationfee and is parent of authorattendeecdregistrationfee.
iasted#IASTED_non_member: iastednonmember is child of delegate who is parent of technicalcommitee.
iasted#Hotel_fee: Hotelfee is a child of fee and money. Tax is a parent of valueaddedtax.
iasted#Fee: The parent of hotelfee is the parent of feeforextratrip and registrationfee. The parent of authorattendeebookregistrationfee is also the parent of tip.
iasted#Publication: The publication of cdproceening and bookproceeding is a child of transportvehicle and car.
iasted#Taxi: The taxi is a child of transportvehicle and shuttlebus.
iasted#Sponsor_state: The sponsor state is the child of the presenter state.
iasted#Reviewer: The child of the reviewer is the child of the speaker and the delegate.
iasted#Review: Review is a child of document which is parented by mailinglist.
iasted#Modelling: Research is the parent of simulating and is the child of modelling.
iasted#Worker_non_speaker: The workernonspeaker is the child of the nonspeaker and the parent of the studentnonspeaker.
iasted#Nonauthor_registration_fee: The nonauthorregistrationfee is a child of registrationfee and is a child of the fee. The parent of sponsorship is the child of the fee.
iasted#Payment_document: The payment document is the parent of cheque and banktransfer. It is also the parent of card and credit card.
iasted#Camera_ready_manuscript_deadline: The camerareadymanuscriptdeadline is the child of the deadline and the parent of the registationdeadline.
iasted#One_conference_day: Oneconferenceday is a child of conferencedays and submissionsdeadline.
iasted#Fee_for_extra_trip: feeforextratrip is a child of fee, which is a parent of tax.
iasted#Full_day_tour: fulldaytour is a child of activityafterconference which is the parent of departure.
iasted#Conference_Hiker: The conferencehiker is a child of a delegate who is also a child of a person.
iasted#Computer: The computer is a child of audiovisualequipment which is a child of an item.
iasted#IASTED_member: The iastedmember is the child of the delegate who is the parent of the sessionchair.
iasted#Memeber_registration_fee: The registrationfee is a child of the registrationfee and the parent of the hotelfee.
iasted#Author_book_proceedings_included: The author of the book "bookproceedings" is the child of the speaker and the parent of the reviewer.
iasted#Sponsor_company_house: The sponsorcompanyhouse is the child of the building which is the parent of the conferencehotel.
iasted#Sponzorship: The parent of the fee is the hotelfee and the child of sponsorship is the parent of the money.
iasted#Student_lecturer: The studentlecturer is the child of the lecturer and the parent of the workerlecturer.
iasted#Trip_city: The city of trinity is the parent of conferencecity.
iasted#Cheque: The payment document, cheque, is the parent of bank transfer.
iasted#Shuttle_bus: The shuttlebus is a child of transportvehicle which is the parent of the van.
iasted#Student_non_speaker: The studentnonspeaker is a child of the nonspeaker and the delegate. The delegate is the parent of the technicalcommitee.
iasted#Student_registration_fee: The student registrationfee is the child of the registrationfee who is the parent of the author attendeebook registrationfee.
iasted#Author_attendee_cd_registration_f: Authorattendeecdregistrationfee is the child of registrationfee and is the parent of authorattendeebookregistrationfee.
iasted#Tip: The child of the sponsor is the child of the money.
iasted#Credit_card: The credit card is the child of the card and the parent of the audiovisual equipment.
iasted#Van: The van is a child of transportvehicle which is the parent of taxi.
iasted#Main_office: The mainoffice is a child of Thing.
iasted#Presenter_university: The presenteruniversity is a child of building which is a child of Thing.
iasted#Departure_tax: The departure tax is a child of tax and money.
iasted#Receiving_manuscript: The child of receivingmanuscript is the child of activitybeforeconference and the parent of refusingmanuscript.
iasted#Double_hotel_room: The doublehotelroom is the child of the homeroom and the parent of the singlehotelroom.
iasted#Initial_manuscipt: The initialmanuscipt is the child of the submission which is the parent of the finalmanuscript.
iasted#Coffee_break: Coffeebreak is a child of conferenceactivity which is parented by lecture and plenarylecture.
iasted#Bank_transfer: The payment document is the child of the bank transfer and the transportvehicle. The transportvehicle is the parent of the car and the transportvehicle is also the child of the payment document.
iasted#Overhead_projector: The overhead projector is a child of audiovisualequipment.
iasted#Speaker_lecture: The speakerlecture is the parent of the plenarylecture and is child of the lecture.
iasted#Coctail_reception: coctailreception is child of conferenceactivity which is parented by presentation and powerpointpresentation.
